<lb n="9" break="no"/>—taṇṭam ce<supplied reason="omitted">y</supplied>tu koṇṭu kuṭuttu Ivvūrkkuḷak
<lb n="10" break="no"/>—ṭṭu <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> Ivvūr <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> Aruḷuvā
